8️⃣ simulate_turn()

=
Simulate one complete turn.

=

FOR each drone:

    IF drone delivered:
        continue

    CHECK next zone

    CHECK occupancy rules

    CHECK connection capacity

    MOVE drone if valid

    OTHERWISE wait
9️⃣ Occupancy system

VERY important.

Subject rules:

max_drones
simultaneous movement
capacity checks

=
Checks if drones can enter zones.

=

FOR target zone:

    COUNT drones inside

    IF capacity exceeded:

        movement invalid
🔟 Restricted movement system

THIS is one of the hardest parts.

Because:

restricted = 2 turns
drone occupies connection during transit

=
Restricted zones require multi-turn movement.

=

IF next zone is restricted:

    SET drone state = TRANSIT

    OCCUPY connection

    WAIT 2 turns

    ARRIVE automatically
1️⃣1️⃣ Connection capacity system

=
Prevent too many drones from using same connection.

=

COUNT drones using connection

IF max_link_capacity exceeded:

    block movement
